<paragraph id="5814433A2D00B842FF32FF6F6991FE18" blockId="2.[166,1225,175,938]" pageId="2" pageNumber="59">
I n c l u d e d s p e c i e s. 
<taxonomicName id="9FAB38B92D00B842FE18FF706EB0FF58" authority="Kretzoi, 1941" authorityName="Kretzoi" authorityYear="1941" box="[497,899,207,234]" class="Mammalia" family="Phocidae" genus="Praepusa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Carnivora" pageId="2" pageNumber="59" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pannonica">
<emphasis id="6ADF9F282D00B842FE18FF706FEDFF5B" box="[497,734,208,233]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="59">Praepusa pannonica</emphasis>
Kretzoi, 1941
</taxonomicName>
, from the early-middle Sarmatian (Middle Miocene) of 
<collectingCountry id="20BC03AA2D00B842FDE8FF4F6F59FEB8" box="[513,618,239,266]" name="Hungary" pageId="2" pageNumber="59">Hungary</collectingCountry>
